<span id="freeTextContainer2903673897126918277"><strong>A distant death</strong><br/><br/>Cadfael must use his skills of deduction to solve a mystery surrounding an unlawful killing and a strange pairing of pilgrims arriving for St Winifred&apos;s festival day at the priory. Why are the two men so close and what do their vows mean? St Winifred also had her own ideas on the miracles that need to happen on her feast day. And Cadfael reveals a secret around one of these. </span>
  <span id="freeText2903673897126918277" style="display:none"><strong>A distant death</strong><br /><br />Cadfael must use his skills of deduction to solve a mystery surrounding an unlawful killing and a strange pairing of pilgrims arriving for St Winifred's festival day at the priory. Why are the two men so close and what do their vows mean? St Winifred also had her own ideas on the miracles that need to happen on her feast day. And Cadfael reveals a secret around one of these. </span>
